{"type":"message","id":"43126ea3","parentId":"16fbe4e3-7eea-4cbc-b913-327e3ae5ce59","timestamp":"2026-05-28T09:25:06.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🍾 捞到一个瓶子！\n📮 ID: BTL-20260528-0001\n📝 内容: \"今天南坪快速通道爆炸了，学校里都闻到味了\"\n💬 回复: 0 条\n\n还没人回这个瓶子呢——要不你回复两句？用 `/回复瓶子 BTL-20260528-0001 你的消息` 就行。🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2052,"output":85,"cacheRead":19200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21337,"cost":{"input":0.00028728,"output":0.000023800000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0005376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008486799999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779960303984,"responseId":"0951d4a8-1c7b-4055-b736-90f4a1570696"}}
