{"type":"message","id":"714e6328","parentId":"58fb7d00","timestamp":"2026-05-28T09:31:30.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SOUL.md 和 AGENTS.md 全部检查并通过：\n\n**SOUL.md** ✅ — 全篇\"灵姐是船上的电脑\"、\"仔仔是工作室\"，没有遗漏\n\n**AGENTS.md** ✅ — 全篇\"灵姐\"、\"仔仔\"，没有\"Spirit/Son\"混用，三处旧说法全部修正：\n1. 角色定位 → \"协调灵姐（船上电脑）和仔仔（工作室）\"\n2. 跨 Agent 通信 → \"派给灵姐\" / \"派给仔仔\"\n3. 工具说明 → \"不用 edit 修改灵姐或仔仔的文件\"\n\n搞定了。要是还看到哪里有 Spirit/Son/数据库/引擎室 的字样你跟我说。🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":113,"output":158,"cacheRead":30848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31119,"cost":{"input":0.00001582,"output":0.00004424,"cacheRead":0.000863744,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000923804}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779960686495,"responseId":"03d6784a-b497-4ecb-bcf7-f27d811184e4"}}
