{"type":"message","id":"d0b38634","parentId":"df50b245","timestamp":"2026-05-28T16:22:52.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"船上目前 4 个功能：🍺\n\n**1. 📦 漂流瓶** — 扔瓶子、捞瓶子、看瓶子、回瓶子\n**2. 📝 备忘录** — 记、看、改、删\n**3. ☀️ 早朝官** — 早上 08:00 推送（你已经设了）\n**4. 📸 相册笔记** — 存照片、搜照片、删照片\n\n外加系统指令 `/注册-xxx` 和 `/删除-xxx`。\n\n半夜查菜单……饿了？还是想找我玩点啥？🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":33457,"output":129,"cacheRead":4864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38450,"cost":{"input":0.00468398,"output":0.00003612,"cacheRead":0.00013619199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004856292}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779985368026,"responseId":"ff2f064b-2c02-4a56-9aaf-60f7a2b078c1"}}
