{"type":"message","id":"bb511ff9","parentId":"9797c15a","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:41:52.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The update can't be run from within the gateway process. I need to stop the gateway first, then update, then restart. But that would kill our conversation. Let me present this to the user and ask how they want to handle it.\n\nFor the image tool path - let me check if there's a way to add workspace-son as an allowed path for the image tool on the Father agent config.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"更新需要停网关才能跑，现在的 session 会断。我来同时处理两个事。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_x0v1Y5jHYEdvDuX01Z4C7974","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查 father 的 agent 配置\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\nfor agent in config.get('agents', {}).get('list', []):\n    if 'father' in agent.get('id','').lower():\n        print(json.dumps(agent, indent=2))\n\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# 查 father 的 agent 配置\\npython3 -c \\\"\\nimport json\\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\\n    config = json.load(f)\\n\\nfor agent in config.get('agents', {}).get('list', []):\\n    if 'father' in agent.get('id','').lower():\\n        print(json.dumps(agent, indent=2))\\n\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":110,"output":229,"cacheRead":72448,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":82,"totalTokens":72787,"cost":{"input":0.0000154,"output":0.00006412,"cacheRead":0.0020285439999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021080639999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779990109067,"responseId":"a85d6db0-6c49-4244-9379-be61bdd694b8"}}
