{"type":"message","id":"e2d812d2","parentId":"ca30de80","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:41:59.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The father agent doesn't have any specific tools config. The image tool restriction is a security feature that restricts file access to the agent's own workspace. This is by design.\n\nFor the Son agent, the image tool (qwen-vl-max-latest) is used from Son's session. When Son runs, it spawns under its own workspace. So the issue is that when I (Father) try to use the image tool on files from Son's workspace, it fails.\n\nThe workaround is fine - copy the image to workspace-father when analysis is needed. But this is a workflow thing, not really a \"fix\".\n\nFor the update: it needs the gateway to be restarted. Since the user just said \"配置56\", they might want me to just note these and we can deal with them later.\n\nLet me summarize the results clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，56 的完整情况：\n\n---\n\n### 5. 🖼️ Image tool 路径\n\n查过了——`image` 工具的安全策略是按 agent 自己的工作目录隔离的。Father 只能读 `workspace-father/` 下的文件。\n\n**不影响正常使用**，因为仔仔（Son）那边 qwen-vl 看图不受影响。只有在**我这边**需要用 image 工具分析图片内容时（比如刚才补 analysis 字段），多一步复制到 workspace-father 就行。这个我已经知道了，以后分析照片我顺手复制一下就好。✅\n\n---\n\n### 6. ⬆️ OpenClaw 更新\n\n`openclaw update` 报错了——因为当前对话跑在网关进程里，更新需要先停网关再跑。如果现在强行更新，**会话会中断**，包括你的早朝定时任务也会重启。\n\n两个选项：\n- **选项A**：我设一个 cron 凌晨没人的时候自动跑更新重启\n- **选项B**：你什么时候方便，手动跑 `openclaw gateway stop && openclaw update && openclaw gateway start`\n\n你选哪个？或者等天亮再说？🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":140,"output":423,"cacheRead":72704,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":173,"totalTokens":73267,"cost":{"input":0.000019600000000000002,"output":0.00011844000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002035712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021737519999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779990112706,"responseId":"f737d597-3b6a-456a-b5d8-cf6676a03526"}}
