{"type":"message","id":"bf24080c","parentId":"8f9e7d0e","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:42:35.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said don't update for now. So I'll leave it as is. Let me wrap up this conversation - it's already 01:42 AM and we've been at this for a while.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，更新先挂着。什么时候想跑跟我说一声就行。\n\n现在已经 01:42 了——你这会儿还折腾吗，还是先收工？我今天修的东西汇总一下：\n\n**今日已完成：**\n- ✅ User.md 绑定 sender_id\n- ✅ Spirit/Son 称谓统一回原名（精神/工作室）\n- ✅ AGENTS.md + SOUL.md 两套文件同步修正\n- ✅ 相册假数据清除（3张 → 1张真图）\n- ✅ `analysis` 字段补上（ALB-20260528-0002）\n- ✅ `photoalbum_function.md` symlink 修复（解决 Spirit ENOENT 错误）\n- ✅ `allowInsecureAuth` 关闭（`true → false`）\n- ✅ 赛博经历 / 分文件结构设计思路已记录\n\n**待办（等你指令）：**\n- ⏳ OpenClaw 更新（2026.5.27）\n- ⏳ 相册视图逻辑改成纯 MEDIA 出图\n- ⏳ User.md 分 sender_id 文件重构 + 赛博经历\n\n走了走了。🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":7740,"output":284,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":42,"totalTokens":73560,"cost":{"input":0.0010836,"output":0.00007952000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001835008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002998128}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779990150847,"responseId":"9267cb44-8391-456d-994a-86811875305a"}}
