{"type":"message","id":"8daf31fa","parentId":"c34b7c39","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:44:25.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see references to `tools.fs.workspaceOnly` but this is about the `read/write/edit/apply_patch` tools, not specifically the `image` tool. The `image` tool has its own path restriction.\n\nLet me check the FAQ about MEDIA paths and workspaceOnly:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_c7g4Am369uPs2fnNO17n0354","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -B5 -A10 \"workspaceOnly.*media\\|MEDIA.*workspace\\|image.*workspace\\|media.*restrict\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md 2>/dev/null | head -40"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -B5 -A10 \\\"workspaceOnly.*media\\\\|MEDIA.*workspace\\\\|image.*workspace\\\\|media.*restrict\\\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md 2>/dev/null | head -40\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1262,"output":160,"cacheRead":89088,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":62,"totalTokens":90510,"cost":{"input":0.00017668000000000002,"output":0.000044800000000000005,"cacheRead":0.002494464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002715944}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779990262936,"responseId":"dad3fc56-ebf1-4614-82f5-f5c8de4e1d7a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7b5e84d","parentId":"8daf31fa","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:44:25.829Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_c7g4Am369uPs2fnNO17n0354","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Also check:\n\n    - The target channel supports outbound media and isn't blocked by allowlists.\n    - The file is within the provider's size limits (images are resized to max 2048px).\n    - `tools.fs.workspaceOnly=true` keeps local-path sends limited to workspace, temp/media-store, and sandbox-validated files.\n    - `tools.fs.workspaceOnly=false` lets `MEDIA:` send host-local files the agent can already read, but only for media plus safe document types (images, audio, video, PDF, and Office docs). Plain text and secret-like files are still blocked.\n\n    See [Images](/nodes/images).\n\n  </Accordion>\n</AccordionGroup>\n\n## Security and access control\n\n<AccordionGroup>\n  <Accordion title=\"Is it safe to expose OpenClaw to inbound DMs?\">"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":92,"aggregated":"Also check:\n\n    - The target channel supports outbound media and isn't blocked by allowlists.\n    - The file is within the provider's size limits (images are resized to max 2048px).\n    - `tools.fs.workspaceOnly=true` keeps local-path sends limited to workspace, temp/media-store, and sandbox-validated files.\n    - `tools.fs.workspaceOnly=false` lets `MEDIA:` send host-local files the agent can already read, but only for media plus safe document types (images, audio, video, PDF, and Office docs). Plain text and secret-like files are still blocked.\n\n    See [Images](/nodes/images).\n\n  </Accordion>\n</AccordionGroup>\n\n## Security and access control\n\n<AccordionGroup>\n  <Accordion title=\"Is it safe to expose OpenClaw to inbound DMs?\">","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779990265827}}
{"type":"message","id":"810c3bf9","parentId":"d7b5e84d","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:44:28.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! So the `tools.fs.workspaceOnly` setting controls whether MEDIA can send files from outside the workspace. But the `image` tool's path restriction is different.\n\nLet me look at the nodes/images doc mentioned in the FAQ.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Zy1gmBOmSVReH6Hv02XM1609","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ -name \"images.md\" -path \"*/nodes/*\" 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"find /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ -name \\\"images.md\\\" -path \\\"*/nodes/*\\\" 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":211,"output":123,"cacheRead":90496,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":51,"totalTokens":90830,"cost":{"input":0.000029540000000000002,"output":0.00003444,"cacheRead":0.0025338879999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025978679999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779990265850,"responseId":"2ec32d08-02b0-4c83-bd43-8c9b2de3ca74"}}
