{"type":"message","id":"d37d8aab","parentId":"668a78ec","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:53:23.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent (Son) has completed the task - the photo was saved successfully. Son also generated the analysis (the Poe-style poem) through its vision model and stored it all in the database.\n\nThe child result shows the image was saved with MEDIA directive. I need to show the image and text to the user. The MEDIA path is `album/images/ALB-20260529-0001.jpg` which is under Son's workspace. But I can still send the MEDIA directive - it's about sending the file, not about the image tool analyzing it.\n\nLet me send the result to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"MEDIA:album/images/ALB-20260529-0001.jpg\n\n📸 **已存 1 张照片！**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n**ID:** ALB-20260529-0001\n**注释:** \"按照图片写一首爱伦坡式的短诗\"\n**标签:** #星海\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n查看全部: `/看相册`\n\n顺便——仔仔用 qwen-vl 看了图，附上爱伦坡风的短诗给你品品：\n\n*星海孤舟·哥特变奏*\n> 墨色的水波，那是夜的叹息，\n> 摇曳着水晶的残骸，\n> 在幽冥的星辰下低语。\n> 一叶孤舟，荡向未名的城垣，\n> 穹顶的光啊——是梦，是魅，\n> 是深渊之上悬荡的金色吊索。\n\n怎么样，有内味吗？🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3574,"output":332,"cacheRead":94208,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":126,"totalTokens":98114,"cost":{"input":0.00050036,"output":0.00009296,"cacheRead":0.002637824,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003231144}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779990797021,"responseId":"df055139-58e7-4fbb-8e57-14b2b0ba9a55"}}
