{"type":"message","id":"0eef1131","parentId":"82164d14","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:59:00.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, images are migrated. Now I need to:\n\n1. Update the database - I'll add a `type` column or change how path is stored. Actually, the `filename` field currently stores just the filename like `ALB-20260528-0002.jpg`. I should keep it as just the filename and use sender_id to construct the path: `images/{sender_id}/{filename}`. That way I don't need to modify existing records.\n\n2. Update Spirit's album_function.md to reflect the new path structure for all operations.\n\n3. Clean up Spirit's old JSON data files - update paths there too.\n\nLet me proceed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VHgYt0QM40uYC7kWtfQa1941","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 更新 Spirit 的 JSON 数据文件（更新图片路径引用）\n# 先看看 Spirit 有哪些文件\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/ -type f 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# 更新 Spirit 的 JSON 数据文件（更新图片路径引用）\\n# 先看看 Spirit 有哪些文件\\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/ -type f 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":171,"output":222,"cacheRead":99840,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":132,"totalTokens":100233,"cost":{"input":0.00002394,"output":0.00006216,"cacheRead":0.00279552,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00288162}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779991137231,"responseId":"97fd4c87-f549-4cc2-9047-bad79a67bd7e"}}
