{"type":"message","id":"a2b5061d","parentId":"8934b817","timestamp":"2026-05-28T17:59:08.296Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit has a parallel directory structure with:\n- `album/data/` - JSON metadata\n- `album/images/` - image files (still has old placeholder 0001 and real 0002)\n\nBut wait - the old ALB-20260528-0001 was the placeholder data I already deleted from Son's database. It's still lingering in Spirit. And ALB-20260528-0001.jpg in Spirit's images is also a placeholder.\n\nLet me:\n1. Clean up Spirit's stale data (delete 0001 placeholder)\n2. Move Spirit's images into user subdirectories too\n3. Update Spirit's JSON data files\n4. Update Spirit's album_function.md","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0Bp6mNFxGILW5DngRa0K7912","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Spirit 也有旧数据需要清理和迁移\n\n# 1. 清理 Spirit 里的占位假数据\nrm -f /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260528-0001.json\nrm -f /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ALB-20260528-0001.jpg\n\n# 2. 创建 Spirit 的用户子目录\nmkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\n\n# 3. 迁移 Spirit 的图片\nmv /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ALB-20260528-0002.jpg /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/\n\n# 4. Spirit 的 JSON 数据文件加上 sender_id 字段\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\n\n# 更新 ALB-20260528-0002.json\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260528-0002.json', 'r') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\n\ndata['sender_id'] = '6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204'\ndata['image']['path'] = 'images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/' + data['image']['filename']\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260528-0002.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(data, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint('Spirit JSON updated ✅')\n\"\n\n# 5. 创建 ALB-20260529-0001.json\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\n\ndata = {\n    'id': 'ALB-20260529-0001',\n    'timestamp': '2026-05-29T01:51:00+08:00',\n    'sender_id': '6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204',\n    'image': {\n        'filename': 'ALB-20260529-0001.jpg',\n        'original_name': 'C9A3F5AACD1FCEA0740AD0696321779D_1779990690028_67d79a.jpg',\n        'size_bytes': 294946,\n        'path': 'images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/ALB-20260529-0001.jpg'\n    },\n    'annotation': '按照图片写一首爱伦坡式的短诗',\n    'tags': ['星海'],\n    'analysis': '',\n    'source': 'qqbot'\n}\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260529-0001.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(data, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint('Spirit 0001 JSON created ✅')\n\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Spirit 最终结构 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/ -type f | sort\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Son 最终结构 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/ -type f | sort"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Spirit 也有旧数据需要清理和迁移\\n\\n# 1. 清理 Spirit 里的占位假数据\\nrm -f /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260528-0001.json\\nrm -f /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ALB-20260528-0001.jpg\\n\\n# 2. 创建 Spirit 的用户子目录\\nmkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\\n\\n# 3. 迁移 Spirit 的图片\\nmv /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ALB-20260528-0002.jpg /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/\\n\\n# 4. Spirit 的 JSON 数据文件加上 sender_id 字段\\npython3 -c \\\"\\nimport json\\n\\n# 更新 ALB-20260528-0002.json\\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260528-0002.json', 'r') as f:\\n    data = json.load(f)\\n\\ndata['sender_id'] = '6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204'\\ndata['image']['path'] = 'images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/' + data['image']['filename']\\n\\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260528-0002.json', 'w') as f:\\n    json.dump(data, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\\n\\nprint('Spirit JSON updated ✅')\\n\\\"\\n\\n# 5. 创建 ALB-20260529-0001.json\\npython3 -c \\\"\\nimport json\\n\\ndata = {\\n    'id': 'ALB-20260529-0001',\\n    'timestamp': '2026-05-29T01:51:00+08:00',\\n    'sender_id': '6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204',\\n    'image': {\\n        'filename': 'ALB-20260529-0001.jpg',\\n        'original_name': 'C9A3F5AACD1FCEA0740AD0696321779D_1779990690028_67d79a.jpg',\\n        'size_bytes': 294946,\\n        'path': 'images/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/ALB-20260529-0001.jpg'\\n    },\\n    'annotation': '按照图片写一首爱伦坡式的短诗',\\n    'tags': ['星海'],\\n    'analysis': '',\\n    'source': 'qqbot'\\n}\\n\\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260529-0001.json', 'w') as f:\\n    json.dump(data, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\\n\\nprint('Spirit 0001 JSON created ✅')\\n\\\"\\n\\necho \\\"\\\"\\necho \\\"=== Spirit 最终结构 ===\\\"\\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/ -type f | sort\\necho \\\"\\\"\\necho \\\"=== Son 最终结构 ===\\\"\\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/ -type f | sort\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":123,"output":976,"cacheRead":100224,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":143,"totalTokens":101323,"cost":{"input":0.00001722,"output":0.00027328000000000004,"cacheRead":0.002806272,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003096772}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779991140727,"responseId":"3334137f-387b-4a0d-ac72-669a9d0f329e"}}
