{"type":"message","id":"7303f7e6","parentId":"fdafb0d3","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:04:04.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The migration isn't fully complete. Let me check:\n\n1. ✅ `images/` directory now has user subdirectories for both users\n2. ❌ Database doesn't have the record for ALB-20260529-0002 - Son didn't insert it\n3. ❌ Spirit doesn't have the JSON for ALB-20260529-0002 - Son didn't create it\n4. ❌ `photos/` directory still exists - Son didn't delete it\n5. ✅ The image file was moved to the correct user subdirectory\n\nSo Son moved the file but didn't complete the database insert or Spirit JSON creation. And the photos/ directory is still there but empty (the file was moved out).\n\nLet me check the subagent result to see what happened, and then fix the remaining parts.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"仔仔搬了文件但还差几步没做完。我收尾。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_XUy6U2Dn2MvuBZHIVCtv2586","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 1. 创建 Spirit JSON\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\n\ndata = {\n    'id': 'ALB-20260529-0002',\n    'timestamp': '2026-05-29T01:22:00+08:00',\n    'sender_id': '346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D',\n    'image': {\n        'filename': 'ALB-20260529-0002.jpg',\n        'original_name': '1779988884595_346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D.jpg',\n        'size_bytes': 137181,\n        'path': 'images/346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D/ALB-20260529-0002.jpg'\n    },\n    'annotation': '',\n    'tags': [],\n    'analysis': '风景照片（1920×874）',\n    'source': 'qqbot'\n}\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ALB-20260529-0002.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(data, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint('Spirit JSON created ✅')\n\"\n\n# 2. 插入数据库\nsqlite3 /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/album.db \"INSERT INTO photos (id,timestamp,sender_id,filename,orig_name,size_bytes,annotation,analysis,tags,source) VALUES ('ALB-20260529-0002','2026-05-29T01:22:00+08:00','346E