{"type":"message","id":"e22b4e9a","parentId":"1453ebba","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:22:11.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is having issues running OpenClaw TUI on their local computer. They're getting permission errors. This seems like a question about their local OpenClaw installation, not about the server where my gateway is running.\n\nLet me think about what could cause \"没有权限\" (no permission) issues with `openclaw tui`:\n\n1. The user might be running it from a different machine and getting permission denied\n2. It could be a filesystem permission issue\n3. It could be a Docker permission issue if they're using Docker\n4. It could be about gateway connection permissions\n\nLet me ask some clarifying questions to understand what specific permission error they're seeing.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"本地连不上 TUI？这个报错信息比较笼统——先确认几个事：\n\n**1. 你是在本机跑 `openclaw tui` 连我这个阿里云上的网关吗？**\n还是你在自己电脑上也装了 OpenClaw？\n\n**2. 具体的报错信息是什么？**\n\"没权限\" 这个范围太大了——是连不上 WebSocket、还是写文件没权限、还是终端报 Permission denied？\n\n**3. 你是用什么方式装的？**\nnpm install、Docker、还是其他？\n\n先给个方向，我帮你定位。🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14433,"output":263,"cacheRead":100224,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":139,"totalTokens":114920,"cost":{"input":0.0020206200000000003,"output":0.00007364,"cacheRead":0.002806272,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004900532}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779992526433,"responseId":"131615f2-4e0e-46e5-ab27-9bdac59736dc"}}
