{"type":"message","id":"3b7b5b02","parentId":"ff571dd5","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:22:47.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying that the server is an Alibaba Cloud (阿里云) server. They're asking about why `openclaw tui` doesn't work on their local computer because they don't have permission.\n\nSince they're connecting to my Alibaba Cloud server, the TUI wouldn't work locally because:\n1. The gateway is running on the remote Alibaba Cloud server, not on their local machine\n2. They'd need to install OpenClaw on their machine or connect via a different method\n\nLet me think about what \"没权限\" really means. The gateway is running on my Alibaba Cloud instance. If they want to use `openclaw tui` locally:\n- Option 1: Install OpenClaw locally and point it to the remote gateway\n- Option 2: Use SSH to access the server and run TUI there\n- Option 3: Use the dashboard web UI\n\nThe \"没权限\" error might be because:\n1. The gateway's WebSocket is bound to loopback (127.0.0.1) by default — not accessible from outside\n2. Or they need to configure Tailscale/tunnel exposure\n3. Or gateway.controlUi settings\n\nLet me check the current gateway bind settings and provide guidance.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了——你本地电脑想用 TUI 连我（阿里云上的网关）？\n\n来查一下当前网关的绑定情况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FnEe1lQUylM7KtWtQSHl8264","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A5 \"gateway\" /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -E \"bind|controlUi|port|tailscale|expose\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -A5 \\\"gateway\\\" /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -E \\\"bind|controlUi|port|tailscale|expose\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6248,"output":366,"cacheRead":108544,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":260,"totalTokens":115158,"cost":{"input":0.0008747200000000001,"output":0.00010248000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003039232,"cacheWri