{"type":"message","id":"5277a071","parentId":"d69d6981","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:22:50.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the full gateway config section.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KmXyKzPlMb4ms8VF7zza5654","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\ngw = config.get('gateway', {})\nprint(json.dumps(gw, indent=2))\n\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"python3 -c \\\"\\nimport json\\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\\n    config = json.load(f)\\ngw = config.get('gateway', {})\\nprint(json.dumps(gw, indent=2))\\n\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":105,"output":107,"cacheRead":115072,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":9,"totalTokens":115284,"cost":{"input":0.000014700000000000002,"output":0.00002996,"cacheRead":0.003222016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003266676}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779992568537,"responseId":"0754a5c9-2937-40f0-bcac-ff874cd1e3f9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bde7ba13","parentId":"5277a071","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:22:50.905Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_KmXyKzPlMb4ms8VF7zza5654","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"mode\": \"local\",\n  \"auth\": {\n    \"mode\": \"token\",\n    \"token\": \"46aeff…9163\"\n  },\n  \"port\": 18789,\n  \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n  \"tailscale\": {\n    \"mode\": \"off\",\n    \"resetOnExit\": false\n  },\n  \"controlUi\": {\n    \"allowInsecureAuth\": false\n  },\n  \"nodes\": {\n    \"denyCommands\": [\n      \"camera.snap\",\n      \"camera.clip\",\n      \"screen.record\",\n      \"contacts.add\",\n      \"calendar.add\",\n      \"reminders.add\",\n      \"sms.send\",\n      \"sms.search\"\n    ]\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":157,"aggregated":"{\n  \"mode\": \"local\",\n  \"auth\": {\n    \"mode\": \"token\",\n    \"token\": \"***\"\n  },\n  \"port\": 18789,\n  \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n  \"tailscale\": {\n    \"mode\": \"off\",\n    \"resetOnExit\": false\n  },\n  \"controlUi\": {\n    \"allowInsecureAuth\": false\n  },\n  \"nodes\": {\n    \"denyCommands\": [\n      \"camera.snap\",\n      \"camera.clip\",\n      \"screen.record\",\n      \"contacts.add\",\n      \"calendar.add\",\n      \"reminders.add\",\n      \"sms.send\",\n      \"sms.search\"\n    ]\n  }\n}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779992570901}}
{"type":"message","id":"67c08cba","parentId":"bde7ba13","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:22:58.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue. The gateway is configured with:\n- `bind: \"loopback\"` — only listens on 127.0.0.1 (localhost)\n- `tailscale.mode: \"off\"` — no tailscale exposure\n- `controlUi.allowInsecureAuth: false` — we just changed this\n\nSo `bind: \"loopback\"` means the gateway WebSocket is only accessible from the server itself. From your local computer, you can't connect to it directly.\n\nOptions for the user:\n1. **Tailscale** — Set up tailscale exposure (`openclaw gateway config set tailscale.mode on` or set `tailscale: { mode: \"on\" }`)\n2. **SSH tunnel** — From local: `ssh -L 18789:127.0.0.1:18789 root@your-server-ip` then local `openclaw tui` connects\n3. **Change bind to LAN** — `openclaw gateway config set gateway.bind lan` or set `bind: \"lan\"` — this exposes to local network (risky without auth + HTTPS)\n4. **Dashboard** — Use the web UI at `http://localhost:18789` if on the server, or via tunnel\n\nActually wait - `openclaw tui` connects to the gateway via WebSocket. If I change `bind` to something accessible, it might work. But the safest approach would be tailscale or SSH tunnel.\n\nThe \"没权限\" error is likely from trying to run `openclaw tui` on their local machine directly without OpenClaw installed, or from trying to connect to the loopback-bound gateway.\n\nLet me give them practical options.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了。网关配置是：\n\n```json\n\"bind\": \"loopback\",     ← 只能从服务器本机连\n\"tailscale\": { \"mode\": \"off\" }\n```\n\n所以 TUI 连不上是正常的——服务器只对自己本机 `127.0.0.1:18789` 开放，你本地电脑当然没权限。\n\n**三个方案：**\n\n### 方案A：SSH 隧道（最简单，我推荐）\n你本地电脑跑：\n```bash\nssh -L 18789:127.0.0.1:18789 root@你的服务器IP\n```\n然后 `openclaw tui` 就能连了。不走公网，安全。\n\n### 方案B：开 Tailscale（安全，但要多装个东西）\n在服务器上 `openclaw gateway config set gateway.tailscale.mode on`，然后在本地也装 Tailscale。两个设备组到同一个 Tailnet 里就能连。\n\n### 方案C：绑定到 LAN（有风险）\n改成 `bind: \"lan\"` 暴露到内网。但阿里云的公网 IP 也能扫到端口，没 HTTPS 的话不太安全。\n\n你选哪个？🍺"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":270,"output":612,"cacheRead":115200,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":359,"totalTokens":116082,"cost":{"input":0.000037800000000000004,"output":0.00017136,"cacheRead":0.0032256,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00343476}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779992570943,"responseId":"2dd936c2-43a4-491e-bd0c-a2521e65523b"}}
