{"type":"message","id":"6675600b","parentId":"db3a2e9b","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:23:08.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"直接npm部署的\" - they deployed OpenClaw via npm install on the server. This means they can just SSH into the server and run `openclaw tui` directly on the server, since it's running locally on the Alibaba Cloud machine.\n\nThe \"没权限\" they mentioned earlier - if they're already SSH'd into the server and running `openclaw tui`, then the issue might be something else. Let me think...\n\nActually, the bind is \"loopback\" which is fine because they're connecting from the server itself. But if they're trying to run it from their local desktop, that's the issue.\n\nWait, \"直接npm部署的\" - this means we (the OpenClaw instance running on this server) was deployed via npm. So the user probably:\n1. Has SSH access to the server\n2. Can SSH in and run commands\n3. But when they try `openclaw tui` locally on their own computer, it doesn't work because the OpenClaw installation is on the server, not on their local machine\n\nOR they SSH into the server and run `openclaw tui` there but get a \"no permission\" error.\n\nGiven the context of the conversation (we're in a QQ bot chat), the user wants to use `openclaw tui` from their local computer to access this server. \n\nThe most practical solution: they should SSH into the server and run `openclaw tui` there, or use SSH tunneling.\n\nActually wait - let me re-read. They said \"我电脑本地无法运行 openclaw tui一直抽风说没权限\" - \"My local computer can't run openclaw tui, keeps saying no permission\".\n\nSo they have OpenClaw installed on their local computer and are trying to use `openclaw tui` to connect to the server's gateway. Since the gateway is bound to loopback, their local TUI can't connect.\n\nThe simplest fix: use SSH port forwarding.\n\nOr better yet - since they npm deployed on the server, they can just SSH into the server and run `openclaw tui` there directly. That's the simplest approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那简单——**直接在服务器上跑 TUI 就行**，不需要本地装。\n\n你 SSH 上服务器之后：\n```bash\nssh root@你的服务器IP\nopenclaw tui\n```\n\nTUI 连的是服务器本机的 `127.0.0.1:18789`，loopback 绑定对这个场景不影响。\n\n如果你想**从自己电脑的 TUI 连过来**，那就需要 SSH 隧道：\n```bash\nssh -L 18789:127.0.0.1:18789 root@你的服务器IP\nopenclaw tui   # 新开一个终端窗口跑\n```\n\n两种方式都行，看你习惯哪种。🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1761,"output":599,"cacheRead":114304,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":456,"totalTokens":116664,"cost":{"input":0.00024654,"output":0.00016772,"cacheRead":0.003200512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003614772}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779992580678,"responseId":"51e478ca-4762-4e7a-9b19-00fa55e11efc"}}
