{"type":"message","id":"63f9f4e2","parentId":"13929e85","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:24:03.396Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they're developing on the server directly (which is what I suggested), but they're getting an error when trying to run `openclaw tui` on the server too. Let me help them debug this.\n\nPossible issues on the server:\n1. The `openclaw` command might not be in PATH for SSH sessions\n2. There might be a node_modules/npm install issue\n3. The TUI might have dependencies that need to be installed\n4. There might be a permissions issue with the terminal/TUI\n\nLet me check what's installed and what command they're running.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哦，服务器上也报错？看看具体什么情况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_WR2yNHbajnzhQGKE0n235937","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which openclaw 2>&1 && openclaw --version 2>&1"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"which openclaw 2>&1 && openclaw --version 2>&1\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1792,"output":196,"cacheRead":114432,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":125,"totalTokens":116420,"cost":{"input":0.00025088000000000004,"output":0.00005488,"cacheRead":0.003204096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003509856}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779992639754,"responseId":"87beb141-f3d3-4783-b80a-9be5c0c33508"}}
