{"type":"message","id":"37e3322f","parentId":"e1d4618b","timestamp":"2026-05-28T18:24:07.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OpenClaw is installed globally. The TUI might have issues - let me check if the TUI dependencies are available (like terminal UI stuff). Let me try to figure out what the actual error is.\n\nThe user said \"服务器上搞也报错了\" - but they didn't give me the specific error message. Let me ask them what the error says, or try to simulate it myself.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ah3HGMJk0AlYT8q1xgsx1164","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 试试 TUI 能不能启动\nopenclaw tui --version 2>&1 || true\n# 检查 TUI 依赖\nnpm list -g openclaw 2>&1 | grep -i tui || true\n# 检查终端类型\necho $TERM\necho $SHELL"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# 试试 TUI 能不能启动\\nopenclaw tui --version 2>&1 || true\\n# 检查 TUI 依赖\\nnpm list -g openclaw 2>&1 | grep -i tui || true\\n# 检查终端类型\\necho $TERM\\necho $SHELL\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":102,"output":190,"cacheRead":116352,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":81,"totalTokens":116644,"cost":{"input":0.00001428,"output":0.000053200000000000006,"cacheRead":0.003257856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003325336}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779992644441,"responseId":"bdba0030-9651-49ea-af26-d861a7d68a26"}}
