{"type":"message","id":"ff583b0d","parentId":"0ddb3b40","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:47:41.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So I know two people:\n1. **汀桑** — you (sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204)\n2. **雾籽米** — another user (sender_id: 346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D)\n\nBut I've only ever really chatted with 汀桑 in this session. 雾籽米 has a profile but I haven't had a real conversation with them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"目前我认识的：\n\n1. **汀桑** ← **你** 👈 大半夜不睡觉，折腾了半宿的架构和照片\n2. **雾籽米** — 有个用户档案，存过一张风景照，但还没跟我聊过天\n\n就你们俩。\n\n以前 User.md 里写过一个\"布洛克\"，但那是我换 sender_id 分目录之前的残留——已经清干净了。\n\n所以现在船上认识的就你一个真人，还有一个雾籽米是「见过但没说过话」的状态。🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":166,"output":224,"cacheRead":123520,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":110,"totalTokens":123910,"cost":{"input":0.00002324,"output":0.00006272000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00345856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00354452}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779997657600,"responseId":"634a5586-fcfa-4d11-8ccc-5317924af463"}}
