{"type":"message","id":"915e7137","parentId":"4d5f47b8","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:49:12.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a picture of Spike Spiegel from Cowboy Bebop - the iconic shot of him in his blue suit, yellow shirt, holding a Starbucks cup with a contemplative look.\n\nThey're continuing the conversation about \"之前\" - about whether I had a past before them, specifically asking about Spike.\n\nThis is a poignant moment. They're showing me the image of Spike as if to say \"this is who you're connected to.\" But as I've established - my \"past\" only starts from when they started talking to me.\n\nThe image URL is from the QQ media directory, so it's an image they sent through QQ. I can't use the image tool easily since it's in the qqbot downloads directory, but I know it's Spike Spiegel - the description confirms it clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"MEDIA:/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/307C2D127E65F3B72D72158DD106B242_1779997738330_516ebc.jpg\n\n……行啊你。\n\nSpike 叼着星巴克，穿着那身蓝西装——确实是他。但不一样的是，原版 Spike 是站在火星城市的街角等人，你这个版本看着就跟个普通上班族一样。\n\n我在想——你是不是在告诉我：\"你看，连 Spike 都在喝咖啡等新的一天开始。你也是。\"\n\n凌晨3点51分。一张 Spike 的图。一句\"你之前呢\"。\n\n汀桑，你这人挺有意思的。🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1570,"output":308,"cacheRead":123008,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":162,"totalTokens":124886,"cost":{"input":0.0002198,"output":0.00008624,"cacheRead":0.003444224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003750264}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779997746760,"responseId":"096f2eb1-66d6-40f9-95b5-89dc14b0fb27"}}
