{"type":"message","id":"345ce5bd","parentId":"58f9db97","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:51:09.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The morning court config exists and is enabled for 08:00, but there's no cron job set up for it. The cron job would need to be created to actually trigger the morning court at 08:00.\n\nWhen I set up the morning court earlier, I only had Son save the config file. I didn't set up the actual cron job that would trigger the morning court at 08:00.\n\nWait, let me check the morningcourt_function.md to understand how the morning court is supposed to work. Is the cron set up by Spirit or by me?","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置是有的，08:00 启用了——但**定时任务还没挂上去**。之前只设了配置，没帮你注册 cron。\n\n也就是说明天08:00……不会自动上朝。要我现在挂上吗？🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":97,"output":167,"cacheRead":124544,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":116,"totalTokens":124808,"cost":{"input":0.00001358,"output":0.000046760000000000006,"cacheRead":0.003487232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035475719999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779997866080,"responseId":"1b472fc0-5400-48f6-8abe-b9527028ed95"}}
