{"type":"message","id":"b887f596","parentId":"feb59d02","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:51:29.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to set up the morning court cron job. Let me check how the morningcourt_function.md defines the cron job setup, and then use the cron tool to create a daily job at 08:00 Asia/Shanghai.\n\nLet me first check what the morning court function says about setting up the cron.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_YyFIvearsHcDnKQJBXZN1244","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A20 \"cron\\|定时\\|每日\\|schedule\" /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -A20 \\\"cron\\\\|定时\\\\|每日\\\\|schedule\\\" /root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/morningcourt_function.md 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1036,"output":144,"cacheRead":123776,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":65,"totalTokens":124956,"cost":{"input":0.00014504,"output":0.00004032,"cacheRead":0.003465728,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003651088}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779997885991,"responseId":"fb0c375f-d248-4a70-a451-6b3efecd7edc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a9438b12","parentId":"b887f596","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:51:29.554Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_YyFIvearsHcDnKQJBXZN1244","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"早朝官：每天早上固定时间自动推送\"早朝简报\"到用户 QQ，包含备忘录待办提醒、漂流瓶海随机瓶子、根据用户画像生成的迷你童话故事、节气饮食建议、当日摄影建议等。用户也可手动触发 `/早朝` 获取即时简报，或调整播报时间、关闭自动播报。\n\n---\n\n## 2. 工作文件夹\n\nSon 在其工作区内创建和维护：\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt/\n```\n\n配置文件存储：`~/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt/config.json`\n\n---\n\n## 3. 触发指令\n\n| 指令 | 参数 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `/早朝` | 无 | 手动触发一次早朝简报 |\n--\n修改 `config-{sender_id}.json` 中的 time 字段，并通知 Father 创建/更新 cron 定时任务。\n\n### 4.4 /关早朝\n\n将 `config-{sender_id}.json` 中的 enabled 设为 false，并通知 Father 移除 cron 定时任务。\n\n---\n\n## 5. 记录格式规范\n\n### config 文件\n\n存储在 morningcourt/ 目录下，按用户独立。文件命名：`config-{sender_id}.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_id\": \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n  \"time\": \"08:00\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-05-28T00:00:00+08:00\"\n}\n```\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":105,"aggregated":"早朝官：每天早上固定时间自动推送\"早朝简报\"到用户 QQ，包含备忘录待办提醒、漂流瓶海随机瓶子、根据用户画像生成的迷你童话故事、节气饮食建议、当日摄影建议等。用户也可手动触发 `/早朝` 获取即时简报，或调整播报时间、关闭自动播报。\n\n---\n\n## 2. 工作文件夹\n\nSon 在其工作区内创建和维护：\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt/\n```\n\n配置文件存储：`~/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt/config.json`\n\n---\n\n## 3. 触发指令\n\n| 指令 | 参数 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `/早朝` | 无 | 手动触发一次早朝简报 |\n--\n修改 `config-{sender_id}.json` 中的 time 字段，并通知 Father 创建/更新 cron 定时任务。\n\n### 4.4 /关早朝\n\n将 `config-{sender_id}.json` 中的 enabled 设为 false，并通知 Father 移除 cron 定时任务。\n\n---\n\n## 5. 记录格式规范\n\n### config 文件\n\n存储在 morningcourt/ 目录下，按用户独立。文件命名：`config-{sender_id}.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_id\": \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n  \"time\": \"08:00\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-05-28T00:00:00+08:00\"\n}\n```\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779997889553}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c9e61c3","parentId":"a9438b12","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:51:33.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! The morningcourt_function.md section 4.3 says:\n\"修改 config-{sender_id}.json 中的 time 字段，并通知 Father 创建/更新 cron 定时任务。\"\n\nSo Spirit is supposed to tell me (Father) to create the cron job. But when I set up the early court earlier, Spirit only sent instructions to Son to save the config, and there was no step to create the cron job.\n\nLet me create the cron job now. The morning court should run daily at 08:00 Asia/Shanghai, and it should trigger an agentTurn for the morning court function.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置早就有了，差的就是这个定时器。挂上。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_cva0Kj6uX8pZdLpwnWaA8816","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 8 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"早朝时间到！用户 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204（汀桑）的早朝播报。请查阅 morningcourt 配置，生成早朝简报并推送给用户。","timeoutSeconds":120},"sessionTarget":"current","enabled":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\": \"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\", \"schedule\": {\"kind\": \"cron\", \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\", \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"}, \"payload\": {\"kind\": \"agentTurn\", \"message\": \"早朝时间到！用户 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204（汀桑）的早朝播报。请查阅 morningcourt 配置，生成早朝简报并推送给用户。\", \"timeoutSeconds\": 120}, \"sessionTarget\": \"current\", \"enabled\": true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":402,"output":348,"cacheRead":124928,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":127,"totalTokens":125678,"cost":{"input":0.00005628,"output":0.00009744,"cacheRead":0.003497984,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003651704}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779997889579,"responseId":"9cfb82dc-6699-431d-8d81-86f2c752b416"}}
