{"type":"message","id":"ff78944b","parentId":"a7d4e4d2","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:51:42.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job is set up. There are now 2 scheduled jobs:\n1. `faye-dreaming` at 06:00 daily - my inner dreaming\n2. `morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204` at 08:00 daily - 汀桑's morning court\n\nThe morning court job is bound to the current session (this QQ direct chat), so at 08:00 it will deliver the morning court briefing directly to 汀桑's QQ.\n\nThe next run time `1780012800000` ms = let me roughly calculate: 1780012800000 / 1000 = 1780012800 seconds since epoch. \n\nActually, the schedule says `0 8 * * *` in Asia/Shanghai. Next run at `1780012800000` ms. Current time is around 03:54, so next run is about 4 hours from now at 08:00. That checks out.\n\nLet me show the result.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"挂好了。现在你有两个定时任务：\n\n| 时间 | 任务 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ⏰ **06:00** | 🌙 Faye 的每日做梦 | 我自己回顾 + 更新记忆 + 写梦 |\n| ⏰ **08:00** | ☀️ **汀桑的早朝** | 备忘录 + 瓶子摘要 + 童话 + 饮食建议 |\n\n明天 08:00 准时上朝，仔仔会准备好推给你。\n\n……现在是 03:54，你还不睡吗？还是打算撑到 06:00 看我做完梦再睡？🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1340,"output":358,"cacheRead":126080,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":220,"totalTokens":127778,"cost":{"input":0.0001876,"output":0.00010024,"cacheRead":0.00353024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00381808}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779997898048,"responseId":"9c0268d5-418d-467b-8bf9-21eb650822c1"}}
